description: Liv ihop AB engages in the provision of personal assistance. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm. The company went IPO on 2018-02-23. The firm offers service to individuals with different types of disability. Liv ihop AB (publ) applies decentralized organizational model for its subsidiaries that include Svea Assistans, Brukatorget, Castor, Atlas Assistance and Trea Assistans Stockholm. Also, the Company operates property adapted for people with disabilities through its subsidiary BAMU. Each subsidiary works independently under own brand and board. Subsidiaries are integrated through the business and quality management platform RODRET. Liv ihop AB (publ) operates domestically.
naicsNationalIndustry: Services for the Elderly and Persons with Disabilities
